/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/workloadmanager/response/response_test.go`\n\n**pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1 tests:**\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agent_type_test.go`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types_test.go`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/constants_test.go`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/groupversion_info_test.go`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types_test.go`\n\n**Other test-related files:**\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/test_spec.md`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/testing/agentcube_tdd_manifest.md`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/coverage.out`\n\n---\n\n## 4. Complete `pkg/` Package Structure\n\n```\npkg/\n|-- apis/runtime/v1alpha1/        # CRD type definitions (AgentRuntime, CodeInterpreter)\n|-- common/types/                  # Common shared types\n|-- picod/                         # PicoD in-sandbox daemon (HTTP server, auth, execute, files)\n|   |-- files/                     # File management subpackage\n|-- router/                        # HTTP router (Gin server, JWT, proxy, session management)\n|-- store/                         # Session store (Redis, Valkey, codec)\n|-- workloadmanager/               # Workload manager (reconciler, handlers)\n    |-- handler/                   # Sandbox lifecycle handlers (create, delete)\n    |-- reconciler/                # Kubernetes reconciler controller\n    |-- response/                  # Response utilities\n```\n\n---\n\n## 5. Key Technology Stack\n\n| Component | Technology |\n|-----------|-----------|\n| Language | Go 1.25.0 |\n| HTTP Framework | Gin v1.10.0 |\n| Kubernetes | client-go v0.34.1, controller-runtime v0.22.2 |\n| Auth | golang-jwt/jwt v5 (RS256) |\n| Storage | go-redis/v9, valkey-go |\n| Testing | stretchr/testify, alicebob/miniredis |\n| Metrics | prometheus/client_golang |\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_28762deeaffeCpf2hZv7X906Bt","model":{"modelID":"qwen3.6-plus","providerID":"alibaba-cn"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore agentcube project structure","time":{"start":1775845056786,"end":1775845229047}}}}
